IApplicationUIFactory
public class DefaultUIFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IApplicationUIFactory

This class is a default factory for ConsoleApplicationUI classes. The ConsoleApplicationUI class displays a modal dialog in text form in the eclipse console.

This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
